trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when an XML document cannot be deserialized into a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> by a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Unntak oppstod under et XML-dokument ikke kan deserialiseres til en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> av en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> throws this exception it supplies a message that describes the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Når den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>oppstår dette unntaket den gir en melding som beskriver hvorfor for unntaket.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: In some cases the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> supplies a list of validation errors and warnings that it encountered while trying to deserialize the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.
trans-unit.target: I noen tilfeller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>inneholder en liste over valideringsfeil og advarsler som den oppstod under deserialisering av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException.ValidationEventArgs%2A> property contains this list if it is supplied.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException.ValidationEventArgs%2A>egenskapen inneholder listen hvis den er oppgitt.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException.ValidationEventArgs%2A>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException"> </xref> klassen med en angitt feilmelding og en referanse til det interne unntaket er årsaken til dette unntaket.

trans-unit.source: An exception that is thrown as a direct result of a previous exception should include a reference to the previous exception in the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Et unntak som er registrert som en direkte resultatet av et tidligere unntak må inkludere en referanse til det tidligere unntaket i den <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is supplied to the constructor or a null reference (Nothing in Visual Basic) if the `innerException` parameter does not supply the inner exception value to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>egenskapen returnerer den samme verdien som er oppgitt til konstruktøren, eller en nullreferanse (ingenting i Visual Basic) Hvis den `innerException` parameteren ikke angi verdien for det indre unntaket til konstruktøren.</xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
trans-unit.target: Unntaket er årsaken til den gjeldende unntaket.

trans-unit.source: If the `innerException` parameter is not a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic), the current exception is raised in a catch block that handles the inner exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `innerException` -parameteren er ikke et nullreferanse (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic), gjeldende unntaket blir opphøyd i en catch-blokk som behandler det interne unntaket.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> object with the collection of <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventArgs"></xref> associated with this exception, and additional exception information.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> objekt med samlingen av <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventArgs"> </xref> som er forbundet med denne unntak og for mer unntaksinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: GetObjectData sets a <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> with all the exception object data targeted for serialization.
trans-unit.target: GetObjectData angir en <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>med alle objektet unntaksdataene mål for serialisering.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>

trans-unit.source: During deserialization the exception object is reconstituted from the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo> transmitted over the stream.
trans-unit.target: Under deserialisering reconstituted unntak-objektet fra den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>overføres via dataflyten.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo>

trans-unit.source: For more information see XML and SOAP Serialization.
trans-unit.target: Se XML og SOAP-serialisering for mer informasjon.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> som inneholder den serialiserte objektdata om som oppstod et unntak.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext> that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>som inneholder kontekstavhengig informasjon om kilden eller målet.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: info is a null reference ( in Visual Basic)
trans-unit.target: infoer en nullreferanse ( i Visual Basic)

trans-unit.source: Gets a list that contains validation warnings and errors associated with this exception.
trans-unit.target: Henter en liste som inneholder Valideringsadvarsler og feil som er knyttet til dette unntaket.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> uses an <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> to deserialize an XML document into a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>Bruker en <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>deserialisering av et XML-dokument i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> collects validation errors and warnings emitted by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>Samler inn valideringsfeil og advarsler slippes ut av <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: At certain points during deserialization, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> determines whether the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> has encountered any validation errors, and, if it has, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> adds these warnings and errors to ValidationEventArgs and throws a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException>.
trans-unit.target: På bestemte tidspunkter under deserialisering, den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>bestemmer om den <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>oppstod disse feilene, og hvis den har, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>legges disse advarsler og feil ValidationEventArgs og oppstår <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> </xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: Not all exceptions of this class will have ValidationEventArgs set.
trans-unit.target: Ikke alle unntak av denne klassen får ValidationEventArgs sett.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.IList> of <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventArgs"></xref> objects that contains validation warnings and errors associated with this exception.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IList>av <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventArgs"> </xref> -objektene Valideringsadvarsler og feil som er knyttet til dette unntaket.</xref:System.Collections.IList>

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty list.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom liste.
